---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'

const pageTitle = 'About the Publication'
const pageDescription = 'A concise introduction to Astrolify Load Test 01 20260522-042729105 and the editorial work it publishes.'
---

<Layout title={pageTitle} description={pageDescription}>
  <article class="ac-generated-page">
    <header class="ac-generated-page__header">
      <p class="ac-generated-page__eyebrow">Pages</p>
      <h1>{pageTitle}</h1>
      <p>{pageDescription}</p>
    </header>

    <section class="ac-generated-page__section">
      <h2>What this publication covers</h2>
      <p>Astrolify Load Test 01 20260522-042729105 exists to publish launch notes, feature explanations, product updates, support-facing information, and related editorial material.</p>
      <p>It is aimed at people evaluating the product, comparing options, or using the service.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="ac-generated-page__section">
      <h2>Editorial standards and selection</h2>
      <p>We prefer clear, practical language and content that helps readers understand the site, its topic, and the surrounding context.</p>
      <p>New pages, revisions, and updates are chosen to keep the site useful even when the brand, team, or business details are still evolving.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="ac-generated-page__section">
      <h2>Publishing scope and ongoing updates</h2>
      <p>Astrolify Load Test 01 20260522-042729105 is expected to publish launch notes, feature explanations, product updates, support-facing information, and related editorial material.</p>
      <p>The site can cover introduce the product, explain the value proposition, and publish supporting product information.</p>
      <p>That usually includes product pages, launch notes, support material, and editorial updates that help people evaluate the service.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="ac-generated-page__section">
      <h2>How updates are handled</h2>
      <p>If a page becomes outdated, it can be revised or replaced without changing the underlying purpose of the site.</p>
      <p>Readers should expect the content to evolve as the publication matures, especially once actual brand details, authors, or contact routes are added.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="ac-generated-page__section">
      <h2>Editorial context for this niche</h2>
      <p>The publication should support product discovery, documentation, and updates without inventing product capabilities or support promises.</p>
    </section>
    <aside class="ac-generated-page__notice">
      <p>This starter page is generated as a baseline and should be reviewed and customized before being relied on as production legal or business copy.</p>
    </aside>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  .ac-generated-page {
    width: min(100% - 2rem, 48rem);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 5rem 0;
  }

  .ac-generated-page__header,
  .ac-generated-page__section,
  .ac-generated-page__notice {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .ac-generated-page__eyebrow {
    color: rgb(var(--ac-primary));
    font-weight: var(--ac-font-semibold);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  }

  .ac-generated-page h1,
  .ac-generated-page h2 {
    color: var(--ac-text);
  }

  .ac-generated-page p {
    color: var(--ac-text-muted);
    line-height: var(--ac-leading-relaxed);
  }

  .ac-generated-page__notice {
    border: 0.0625rem solid var(--ac-border-color);
    border-radius: var(--ac-rounded-xl);
    padding: 1rem;
    background: var(--ac-bg-subtle);
  }
</style>
